155 typedef struct GEOSContextHandle_HS
156 {
157  const GeometryFactory *geomFactory;
158  char msgBuffer[1024];
159  GEOSMessageHandler noticeMessageOld;
160  GEOSMessageHandler_r noticeMessageNew;
161  void *noticeData;
162  GEOSMessageHandler errorMessageOld;
163  GEOSMessageHandler_r errorMessageNew;
164  void *errorData;
165  int WKBOutputDims;
166  int WKBByteOrder;
167  int initialized;
168 
169  GEOSContextHandle_HS()
170  :
171  geomFactory(0),
172  noticeMessageOld(0),
173  noticeMessageNew(0),
174  noticeData(0),
175  errorMessageOld(0),
176  errorMessageNew(0),
177  errorData(0)
178  {
179  memset(msgBuffer, 0, sizeof(msgBuffer));
180  geomFactory = GeometryFactory::getDefaultInstance();
181  WKBOutputDims = 2;
182  WKBByteOrder = getMachineByteOrder();
183  setNoticeHandler(NULL);
184  setErrorHandler(NULL);
185  initialized = 1;
186  }

231  void
232  NOTICE_MESSAGE(string fmt, ...)
233  {
234  if (NULL == noticeMessageOld && NULL == noticeMessageNew) {
235  return;
236  }
237 
238  va_list args;
239  va_start(args, fmt);
240  int result = vsnprintf(msgBuffer, sizeof(msgBuffer) - 1, fmt.c_str(), args);
241  va_end(args);
242 
243  if (result > 0) {
244  if (noticeMessageOld) {
245  noticeMessageOld("%s", msgBuffer);
246  } else {
247  noticeMessageNew(msgBuffer, noticeData);
248  }
249  }
250  }
251 
252  void
253  ERROR_MESSAGE(string fmt, ...)
254  {
255  if (NULL == errorMessageOld && NULL == errorMessageNew) {
256  return;
257  }
258 
259  va_list args;
260  va_start(args, fmt);
261  int result = vsnprintf(msgBuffer, sizeof(msgBuffer) - 1, fmt.c_str(), args);
262  va_end(args);
263 
264  if (result > 0) {
265  if (errorMessageOld) {
266  errorMessageOld("%s", msgBuffer);
267  } else {
268  errorMessageNew(msgBuffer, errorData);
269  }
270  }
271  }
272 } GEOSContextHandleInternal_t;

295 char* gstrdup_s(const char* str, const std::size_t size)
296 {
297  char* out = static_cast<char*>(malloc(size + 1));
298  if (0 != out)
299  {
300  // as no strlen call necessary, memcpy may be faster than strcpy
301  std::memcpy(out, str, size + 1);
302  }
303 
304  assert(0 != out);
305 
306  // we haven't been checking allocation before ticket #371
307  if (0 == out)
308  {
309  throw(std::runtime_error("Failed to allocate memory for duplicate string"));
310  }
311 
312  return out;
313 }

315 char* gstrdup(std::string const& str)
316 {
317  return gstrdup_s(str.c_str(), str.size());
318 }

324 GEOSContextHandle_t
325 initGEOS_r(GEOSMessageHandler nf, GEOSMessageHandler ef)
326 {
327  GEOSContextHandle_t handle = GEOS_init_r();
328 
329  if (0 != handle) {
330  GEOSContext_setNoticeHandler_r(handle, nf);
331  GEOSContext_setErrorHandler_r(handle, ef);
332  }
333 
334  return handle;
335 }

759 char
760 GEOSRelatePatternMatch_r(GEOSContextHandle_t extHandle, const char *mat,
761  const char *pat)
762 {
763  if ( 0 == extHandle )
764  {
765  return 2;
766  }
767 
768  GEOSContextHandleInternal_t *handle = 0;
769  handle = reinterpret_cast<GEOSContextHandleInternal_t*>(extHandle);
770  if ( 0 == handle->initialized )
771  {
772  return 2;
773  }
774 
775  try
776  {
777  using geos::geom::IntersectionMatrix;
778 
779  std::string m(mat);
780  std::string p(pat);
781  IntersectionMatrix im(m);
782 
783  bool result = im.matches(p);
784  return result;
785  }
786  catch (const std::exception &e)
787  {
788  handle->ERROR_MESSAGE("%s", e.what());
789  }
790  catch (...)
791  {
792  handle->ERROR_MESSAGE("Unknown exception thrown");
793  }

4633 GEOSGeometry *
4634 GEOSGeom_setPrecision_r(GEOSContextHandle_t extHandle, const GEOSGeometry *g,
4635  double gridSize, int flags)
4636 {
4637  using namespace geos::geom;
4638 
4639  assert(0 != g);
4640 
4641  if ( 0 == extHandle )
4642  {
4643  return NULL;
4644  }
4645 
4646  GEOSContextHandleInternal_t *handle = 0;
4647  handle = reinterpret_cast<GEOSContextHandleInternal_t*>(extHandle);
4648  if ( 0 == handle->initialized )
4649  {
4650  return NULL;
4651  }
4652 
4653  try
4654  {
4655  const PrecisionModel *pm = g->getPrecisionModel();
4656  double cursize = pm->isFloating() ? 0 : 1.0/pm->getScale();
4657  std::unique_ptr<PrecisionModel> newpm;
4658  if ( gridSize ) newpm.reset( new PrecisionModel(1.0/gridSize) );
4659  else newpm.reset( new PrecisionModel() );
4660  GeometryFactory::Ptr gf =
4661  GeometryFactory::create( newpm.get(), g->getSRID() );
4662  Geometry *ret;
4663  if ( gridSize && cursize != gridSize )
4664  {
4665  // We need to snap the geometry
4666  GeometryPrecisionReducer reducer( *gf );
4667  reducer.setPointwise( flags & GEOS_PREC_NO_TOPO );
4668  reducer.setRemoveCollapsedComponents( ! (flags & GEOS_PREC_KEEP_COLLAPSED) );
4669  ret = reducer.reduce( *g ).release();
4670  }
4671  else
4672  {
4673  // No need or willing to snap, just change the factory
4674  ret = gf->createGeometry(g);
4675  }
4676  return ret;
4677  }
4678  catch (const std::exception &e)
4679  {
4680  handle->ERROR_MESSAGE("%s", e.what());
4681  }
4682  catch (...)
4683  {
4684  handle->ERROR_MESSAGE("Unknown exception thrown");
4685  }
4686 
4687  return NULL;
4688 }
